thread.title: Benjamin Le
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Benjamin Le

author: Benjamin Le
title: Benjamin Le
text:
I called the Sydney store whom picked up promptly and confirmed that the audio equipment was in stock. I visited the store the same day and received fantastic service.
Although the staff sensed I knew about my products, it would have been great if they asked me what my goals were for purchasing the equipment and see how they could advise.
